{"tid":1516044,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［集合年登廚神］研發林奠油炸鬼 幫林奠遺臭萬年","createTime":"2019-08-29T11:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T17:03:02.000Z","uid":314590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d82ecae1b18bfb088515db1c2e08a0d54154da48","tid":1516044,"uid":314590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"｛食油炸鬼忽發奇想｝不如幫林奠諗種好食又易整既食物 好似油炸鬼咁 令世世代代既香港人都記得林奠出賣香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>油炸鬼典故</strong><br />\n油炸鬼原本係叫做油炸檜；檜即係宋朝嗰陣一個被公認為奸相嘅秦檜；而油炸檜就係後人因為勁憎呢個奸相曾經設計陷害忠臣岳飛，恨佢做禍國殃民嘅事，於是創作呢種民間小食嚟發洩，寓意秦檜同佢老婆死咗之後除咗希望佢哋落地獄之外，重要俾閰羅王放佢哋落滾油度炸嚟懲罰佢。由於係咒佢哋兩公婆，所以油炸鬼一定係好似有兩條嗤埋咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴絲打米芝蓮廚神 快d幫手諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好有埋食譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4382483fd57f1d29670edea03cfdc7538161faa","tid":1516044,"uid":234998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77fa11ea2d4c0f9df987165a67e5c4fd1cba780a","tid":1516044,"uid":314590,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d82ecae1b18bfb088515db1c2e08a0d54154da48","tid":1516044,"uid":314590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:56:56.000Z","msg":"｛食油炸鬼忽發奇想｝不如幫林奠諗種好食又易整既食物 好似油炸鬼咁 令世世代代既香港人都記得林奠出賣香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>油炸鬼典故</strong><br />\n油炸鬼原